#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Введение"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kanagram; is a game based on anagrams of words: the puzzle is solved "
#| "when the letters of the scrambled word are put back in the correct order. "
#| "There is no limit on either time taken, or the amount of attempts to "
#| "solve the word. Included with &kanagram; are several vocabularies ready "
#| "to play, with many more available from the Internet."
msgid ""
"&kanagram; is a game based on anagrams of words: the puzzle is solved when "
"the letters of the scrambled word are put back in the correct order. There "
"is no limit on either time taken, or the number of attempts to solve the "
"word. Included with &kanagram; are several vocabularies ready to play, with "
"many more available from the Internet."
msgstr ""
"Игроку предлагается набор букв в произвольном порядке, из которого он должен "
"составить слово. Задание даётся без ограничения по времени и числу попыток. "
"Несколько словарей уже встроено в &kanagram;. Дополнительные словари "
"возможно автоматически загрузить через Интернет или создать самостоятельно."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kanagram;"
msgstr "Использование &kanagram;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &kanagram;, showing "
#| "the main interface to the application. Much of the window is taken up by "
#| "the <interface>blackboard</interface>, where the puzzles are written "
#| "onto, with the <interface>filing cabinet</interface> on the right "
#| "containing application controls:"
msgid ""
"Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &kanagram;, showing the "
"main interface to the application. Much of the window is taken up by the "
"<interface>blackboard</interface>, where the puzzles are written, with the "
"<interface>filing cabinet</interface> on the right containing application "
"controls."
msgstr ""
"Так выглядит окно игры сразу после запуска &kanagram;. Большую часть экрана "
"занимает <interface>доска</interface>, на ней показываются анаграммы. Справа "
"расположена <interface>картотека</interface>, содержащая элементы управления "
"игрой."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here is the screen that is presented on startup of &kanagram;"
msgstr "Так выглядит окно игры сразу после запуска &kanagram;"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:77 index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kanagram; screenshot"
msgstr "Снимок экрана &kanagram;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <interface>Vocabulary Switcher</interface> (<keysym>PgUp</keysym> / "
#| "<keysym>PgDown</keysym>) allows the user to quickly <action>change the "
#| "active vocabulary</action> by clicking with the &LMB; on the arrows to "
#| "<action>advance to the next vocabulary</action> or to <action>return to "
#| "the previously-played vocabulary</action>."
msgid ""
"The <interface>Vocabulary Switcher</interface> (&PgUp; / &PgDn;) allows the "
"user to quickly <action>change the active vocabulary</action> by clicking "
"with the &LMB; on the arrows to <action>advance to the next vocabulary</"
"action> or to <action>return to the previously-played vocabulary</action>."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Переключатель словарей</interface> (<keysym>PgUp</keysym> / "
"<keysym>PgDown</keysym>) позволяет быстро <action>сменить текущий словарь</"
"action>, щёлкнув левой кнопкой мыши по соответствующей стрелке для "
"<action>перехода к следующему</action> или <action>возврата к предыдущему "
"словарю</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the center of the <interface>blackboard</interface> is the anagram puzzle "
"to be solved."
msgstr "Анаграммы показываются в центре <interface>доски</interface>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This is the <guiicon>Start Timer</guiicon> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
#| "\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) button, and allows you to "
#| "<action>start or stop scoring timer</action>."
msgid ""
"This is the <guiicon>Start Timer</guiicon> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) button, and allows you to <action>start or "
"stop the scoring timer</action>."
msgstr ""
"Кнопка <guiicon>Запустить таймер</guiicon> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo>) позволяет <action>запускать или останавливать "
"таймер для начисления очков</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the <guibutton>Hint</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>) button is clicked, a short sentence will "
"appear, <action>describing the current word puzzle</action>."
msgstr ""
"При нажатии кнопки <guibutton>Показать подсказку</guibutton> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo>) <action>показывается "
"краткое описание загаданного слова</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guibutton>Reveal Word</guibutton> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>) button <action>solves the current word "
"puzzle</action>."
msgstr ""
"При нажатии кнопки <guibutton>Показать ответ</guibutton> (<keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>) <action>показывается разгадка "
"анаграммы</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Entry Box</interface> allows you to <action>input your "
"attempts</action> to solve the current word puzzle."
msgstr ""
"<interface>Поле ввода</interface> служит для <action>ввода ответа</action>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <interface>Next Anagram</interface> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) button lets you switch to the next guess."
msgstr ""
"При нажатии кнопки <interface>Следующая анаграмма</interface> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>) показывается следующее "
"загаданное слово."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the <guiicon>Configure</guiicon> button, which <action>opens the "
"<guilabel>Configure</guilabel> &kanagram; dialog</action>."
msgstr ""
"Это кнопка <guiicon>Настроить</guiicon>. При нажатии этой кнопки "
"<action>открывается диалоговое окно <guilabel>Настройка</guilabel> программы "
"&kanagram;</action>."

