#: index.docbook:124
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guiicon>Help</guiicon> button is special, in that it <action>reveals "
#| "3 sub-buttons</action>. These buttons are shown when the <guiicon>Help</"
